      "verdict": "unverifiable",
      "explanation": "Engin heimild í staðreyndagrunni staðfestir hver er formaður Evrópuhreyfingarinnar. Heimildir fjalla um stjórnmálaflokka (<a href=\"https://www.althingi.is/thingmenn/thingflokkar/vidreisn/\" title=\"Althingi — Session 157; Viðreisn party platform\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">POLITICAL-DATA-004</a>, <a href=\"https://www.midflokkurinn.is/\" title=\"Miðflokkurinn — Party website and statements; ECR Party membership; Icelandic media reports\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">POLITICAL-DATA-013</a>), framkvæmdastjórn ESB (<a href=\"https://commission.europa.eu/strategy-and-policy/priorities-2019-2024/stronger-europe-world/ethics-and-integrity/code-conduct-commissioners_en\" title=\"Article 245 TFEU; European Commission Code of Conduct for Commissioners (C(2018) 700); European Ombudsman Decision OI/1/2021/KR\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">SOV-LEGAL-023</a>) og ýmis hagsmunasamtök (<a href=\"https://sa.is/frettatengt/frettir/vinna-hafin-vid-uttekt-a-stodu-adildarvidraedna-vid-evropusambandid\" title=\"SA — 'Iceland and Europe: The Business Case' (2025); SA annual congress resolutions\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">POL-DATA-012</a>, <a href=\"https://en.rannis.is/funding/research/\" title=\"University of Iceland — Rector's statement on EU membership; Rannís — Horizon Europe participation data\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">POL-DATA-018</a>), en Evrópuhreyfingin (European Movement Iceland) er ekki nefnd sérstaklega. Fullyrðingin krefst heimildar um formannskap þess tiltekna samtaka.",
      "missing_context": "Staðreyndagrunnurinn inniheldur ekki upplýsingar um Evrópuhreyfinguna á Íslandi eða forystu hennar. Þyrfti beina heimild um samtökin og formannskap þeirra.",
